    <item>
      <title>Playstation UI</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/385841</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">cd5e052a817ce9633237ffda89bd96377f24b661</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 00:54:43 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62b9a7c060e4b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62b99f9dc8a4a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62b99f9db6455.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62b9be087cbee.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62b8b1f08b0e7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62b9c19d89411.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Added IT, ES, FR support&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: added IT, ES, FR support&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: fixed a not swapped button texture when using the swapped layout&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a mod that replaces the default Nintendo layout with Playstation buttons.&lt;br&gt;Currently, it supports the &lt;b&gt;EU (EN, DE, FR, IT, ES)&lt;/b&gt; as well as the &lt;b&gt;US (EN)&lt;/b&gt; version of the game.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;To install, simply extract the included folder into the graphicsPacks folder of your Cemu install and enable the Mod in Cemu's Graphics Packs settings.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This also includes a version that swaps the functionalities of the X and O button, mirroring a more traditional western button layout with the main interact button being X (see pictures). For this to work, you need to swap the controls for A &amp;amp; B in Cemu's input settings.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The R1 button only shows R during gameplay. I could edit it to R1 but since that label is limited to a single character in width, it looks pretty crammed in there. Textboxes show R1.&lt;br&gt;Also, I did all the necessary research and editing in a day so&amp;nbsp;if you happen to find any other places with the wrong buttons, please write a comment.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/windwakerhd_ps_ui_591f9.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/windwakerhd_ps_ui_swapped_a2747.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <category>Other/Misc</category>
      <category>Game files</category>
    </item>
