    <item>
      <title>Beta-styled Link</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/436709</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">fc1f82763b448090df57276797645afd5ad52d4d</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Apr 2023 15:31:29 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64303625c8caf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64303627694bc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64303628863a4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/643036277008c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/643036264c191.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/643036264be82.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6430362475c1f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/643036248d284.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6430362756556.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/643036273cd44.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Recolors Link's outfit (and optionally eyes) to resemble beta screenshots and footage.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;Comes with an optional extra mod to remove the aiming reticles&lt;/span&gt;. (There's no easy way to merge modded package files, unfortunately)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Install&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;-----&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Wii U Console&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-----&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;TO BE USED WITH THE AROMA MODDING ENVIRONMENT &amp;amp; SDCAFIINE&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;https://aroma.foryour.cafe/&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-----&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Install (US version):&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Place the wiiu folder at the root of your SD card. RENAME one or more of the pack files to choose which version&amp;nbsp;of the mod you wish to use (for example, for the beta outfit but regular eyes, rename "permanent_3d_beta" to&amp;nbsp;"permanent_3d"). Once you have made sure you are booted into Aroma, just launch the game! With Aroma, you can&amp;nbsp;launch a specific mod pack, but if this is your only one it will launch it straight away.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Install (non-US region):&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Rename the titleid for the mod folder to your region.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;EU folder name: 0005000010143600&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;JP folder name: 0005000010143400&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-----&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;CEMU&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-----&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Place the graphics pack into CEMU's graphics pack folder, RENAME one or more of the pack files to choose which&amp;nbsp;version of the mod you wish to use (for example, for the beta outfit but regular eyes, rename&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;"permanent_3d_beta" to "permanent_3d") then enable it in the settings.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/betalink_for_wwhd.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
