    <item>
      <title>Playable Tetra</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/414984</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">cd9089e9d6f16fc53979d24710da0f443506954b</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Dec 2022 19:43:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63c5b99d93de0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63d2f77f987f9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63d2f7807d10e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63d2f780b0bd8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63d2f780d6b55.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63e2b4ba9ef61.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63e2b4bbe08d5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Description:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There's 4 files here.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. wwhd playable Tetra: This lets you play as Tetra. The female dialogue patch is included.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. wwhd NPC Link over Tetra: A Link model that replaces the NPC version of Tetra. Be warned that there is no male audio or dialogue for this mod yet, so the other pirates will still say "Miss Tetra" when referring to their captain, and you'll hear Tetra's high-pitched voice coming from Link's mouth.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. wwhd Princess Link: Princess Zelda's head is replaced with Link's.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. wwhd Princess Link (green): Same as the mod above, but the dress matches the color's of Link's hero's clothes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Installation:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Download and unpack this mod and then place it into the graphics packs folder within your Cemu Folder. Open Cemu &amp;gt; Options &amp;gt; Graphic packs &amp;gt; Wind Waker HD &amp;gt; Mods &amp;gt; check off the mod. Now you can play the game.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you want to install this on your WiiU, use this tutorial:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/15380"&gt;https://gamebanana.com/tuts/15380&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Thanks:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Many thanks to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1701022"&gt;SariaOfTheKokiri&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for her &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/13636"&gt;Custom Character Tutorial&lt;/a&gt;, and her &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/50002" class="SelectedElement"&gt;Female Dialogue Patch&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;And thank you to the creators of the &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AuI9OHi6Ni2HUzyBf_djT5wa1gzVmN2SG3jbROtrFKw/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"&gt;GameCube Model Tutorial&lt;/a&gt; which works great with the WiiU version as well.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Recommended Mod:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you'd like more immersion with this mod, go ahead and include this mod:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/sounds/64799"&gt;Linkle Voice Mod&lt;/a&gt;. It's not quite the same as Tetra's voice, but it's much more believable than playing as Tetra with Link's voice.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/wwhd_playable_tetra_mod_3787f.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/wwhd_npc_link_over_tetra.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/wwhd_princess_link.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/wwhd_princess_link_green__b4015.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
      <category>Zelda/Tetra</category>
      <category>Skins</category>
    </item>
    <item>
