      <guid isPermaLink="false">bc9befc784032630fa1bed3012ef3630ede0cdc6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Nov 2022 22:03:34 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/637e96ab9c728.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/637e96b355875.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/637e96b368516.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod allows you to play as Link in his casual clothes without having to beat the entire game first. Alternatively, you could download a save file of a completed game from somebody else, but here's a mod for those of you who aren't familiar with importing save files.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Many thanks to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1701022"&gt;SariaOfTheKokiri&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for her custom character tutorial:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/13636"&gt;https://gamebanana.com/tuts/13636&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;And thank you to the creators of the GameCube Model Tutorial which works great with the WiiU version too:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AuI9OHi6Ni2HUzyBf_djT5wa1gzVmN2SG3jbROtrFKw/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"&gt;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AuI9OHi6Ni2HUzyBf_djT5wa1gzVmN2SG3jbROtrFKw/edit?usp=sharing&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Installation:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Download and unpack this mod and then place it into the graphics packs folder within your Cemu Folder. Then, once you open Cemu, click on options &amp;gt; graphics packs &amp;gt; Wind Waker HD &amp;gt; Mods &amp;gt; check off the mod. Now you can play the game.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you want to install this on your WiiU, use this tutorial:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/15380"&gt;https://gamebanana.com/tuts/15380&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/casual_clothes_mod_fb8f3.7z" type="application/x-7z-compressed"/>
      <category>Link</category>
      <category>Skins</category>
    </item>
    <item>
