      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Nov 2022 20:42:56 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/637e81af3a891.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/637e81c302aee.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/637e81cfe067e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/637e81d65825a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod allows you to play as Link in his hero's clothes without a hat.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Many thanks to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1701022"&gt;SariaOfTheKokiri&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for her custom character tutorial:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/13636"&gt;https://gamebanana.com/tuts/13636&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;And thank you to the creators of the GameCube Model Tutorial which works great with the WiiU version too: &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AuI9OHi6Ni2HUzyBf_djT5wa1gzVmN2SG3jbROtrFKw/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"&gt;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AuI9OHi6Ni2HUzyBf_djT5wa1gzVmN2SG3jbROtrFKw/edit?usp=sharing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Instructions:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Download and unpack this mod and then place it into the graphics packs folder within your Cemu Folder. Then, once you open Cemu, click on options &amp;gt; graphics packs &amp;gt; Wind Waker HD &amp;gt; Mods &amp;gt; check Hatless Link. Now you can play the game.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you want to install this on your WiiU, use this tutorial:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/15380"&gt;https://gamebanana.com/tuts/15380&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
